    sinDatosAncestros:'ANCESTOR DATA NOT PROVIDED', ciclosFractalesLabel:'FRACTAL CYCLES',
    lealtadesBody:'With Voltage {voltajeA} ({archNom}), {name} carries the ancestral mandate: "{conflicto}". This programme has been running since the first ancestor who lived it without resolving it. An invisible loyalty is not a conscious decision — it is a survival instruction installed in the emotional field of the clan. The hardware is configured to express "{don}", but the inherited distortion activates "{herida}" whenever the tree detects a real expansion risk. The tree interprets growth as a betrayal to the group and activates the handbrake.',
