    sinDatosEspejos:'NO DATA TO CALCULATE MIRRORS',
    sinResonanciaDetallada:'No direct resonance detected with the consultant in this protocol',
    espejosPgBody:'{name} (V{voltajeA} {grupo}), the tree\'s search engine has detected {n} active resonance(s) between you and your lineage. Each mirror is an active duplication protocol: the tree does not create coincidences, it executes instructions. A IDENTICAL VOLTAGE mirror means the ancestor lived exactly the same core conflict — your wound is a direct repetition. A COMPLEMENTARY PAIR (sum = 9) is the maximum Tesla tension: two opposing frequencies that need each other to complete the cycle. MIRROR CYCLES mark the exact years where the transgenerational pressure on {name} reaches its peak.',
    codigoArquetipico:'ARCHETYPAL CODE — NUMERICAL TABLE OF THE LINEAGE',
    codigoArqDesc:'The active voltages in your tree determine which conflicts and gifts each line carries. The highlighted ones are your actual field.',
