    escaleraFractalPadre:'FATHER\'S FRACTAL LADDER', espejoConConsultante:'MIRROR WITH CONSULTANT',
    lineaPaternaBodyBase:'The paternal lineage is the electrical line of {name}\'s system: it transmits the voltage of boundaries, authority, the permission to exist and occupy space in the world.',
