    escaleraFractalMadre:'MOTHER\'S FRACTAL LADDER',
    lineaMaternaBodyBase:'The maternal lineage is the magnetic line of {name}\'s system: it transmits the frequency of the nest, nourishment, emotional security and the permission to receive.',
    lineaMaternaBodyConMadre:' The mother carries Voltage {voltM} — archetype "{archM}" ({grupoM}). Her natural gift was "{donM}", but her active wound was "{heridaM}". The polarity between mother and child is ',
    lineaMaternaBodyPolarIdent:'IDENTICAL ({grupoM}) — risk of emotional fusion without identity differentiation: the maternal field and the consultant\'s field vibrate at the same frequency',
    lineaMaternaBodyPolarOp:'OPPOSITE — support and emotional complement structure: the magnetic line contributes what the consultant\'s native frequency does not generate spontaneously',
