    anilloAbueloPat:'IN-DEPTH ANALYSIS — SECOND RING: PATERNAL GRANDFATHER', sinAbueloPat:'PATERNAL GRANDFATHER\'S DATE NOT PROVIDED',
    espejoConsultante:'CONSULTANT MIRROR',
    anilloAbueloPatBody:'The paternal grandfather is the first cell of {name}\'s patrilineal lineage. His voltage and nodes define the father\'s original software. When a paternal grandfather\'s node coincides with a node of {name}, the unresolved conflict transmission has skipped a generation: the father acted as a passive channel and the system deposited it directly into {name}. These nodes in green are patrilineal second-ring liberation windows.',
    anilloAbuelaPat:'IN-DEPTH ANALYSIS — SECOND RING: PATERNAL GRANDMOTHER', sinAbuelaPat2:'PATERNAL GRANDMOTHER\'S DATE NOT PROVIDED',
    anilloAbuelaPatBody:'The paternal grandmother carries the emotional software of the patrilineal lineage. Her voltage defines the attachment pattern and the base emotional wound transmitted through {name}\'s father. The paternal grandmother\'s nodes that coincide with {name}\'s reveal the feminine transgenerational wound of the paternal electrical line — frequently related to the blocked gift that {name} must release.',
    anilloAbuMaterno:'IN-DEPTH ANALYSIS — SECOND RING: MATERNAL GRANDFATHER', sinAbuMaterno:'MATERNAL GRANDFATHER\'S DATE NOT PROVIDED',
    anilloAbuMaternoBody:'The maternal grandfather is the first cell of the patrilineal lineage of {name}\'s maternal line. His voltage defines the software of origin of the mother\'s masculine lineage. When a maternal grandfather\'s node coincides with {name}\'s node, the mother\'s unresolved paternal wound is transmitted directly — a double load of unprocessed conflict that increases the pressure on {name} as the system\'s cleanup terminal.',
    anilloAbuMaterna:'IN-DEPTH ANALYSIS — SECOND RING: MATERNAL GRANDMOTHER', sinAbuMaterna2:'MATERNAL GRANDMOTHER\'S DATE NOT PROVIDED',
    anilloAbuMaternaBody:'The maternal grandmother is the first matrilineal cell of {name}\'s system. Her voltage defines the emotional base software of the maternal line: the primary attachment pattern, the identity wound and the survival conflict. The maternal grandmother\'s nodes that coincide with {name}\'s activate the deepest layer of the system — the biological programming of origin, the first frequency that {name}\'s organism received when forming in the maternal field.',
    diagBiologico:'BIOLOGICAL DIAGNOSIS — CONSULTANT CODE',
    diagBiologicoBody:'{name}, your body speaks the language of your Voltage {voltajeA}. The inherited ancestral distortion manifests biologically through the {terminal} terminal. The body does not get ill by chance — it is the last hardware available to store the surplus voltage that was not processed in the emotional or mental field. The root conflict of the lineage carried by {name} is: "{conflicto}". This pattern is not personal — it is an active frequency inheritance. Every chronic symptom in the biological terminal is a system alert warning that the conflict remains unresolved. By recognising the origin, {name} activates the repolarisation process: transforming "{herida}" into the genuine expression of the gift "{archNom}": "{don}".',
    arquetipoActivo:'ACTIVE ARCHETYPE OF THE CONSULTANT', donEnCoherencia:'GIFT IN COHERENCE',
    heridaEnDistorsion:'WOUND IN DISTORTION', terminalBiologico:'BIOLOGICAL TERMINAL',
    conflictoAncestral:'ANCESTRAL ROOT CONFLICT OF THE LINEAGE',
    repolarizacion:'REPOLARISATION: Identify the ancestor who originated the conflict and honour their fate without repeating it.',
    arquetiposHeredados:'INHERITED ARCHETYPES FROM THE LINEAGE',
    conflictosCruzados:'CROSS CONFLICTS — CLAN TENSION MAP',
    conflictosCruzadosBody:'Each pair of lineage members with different voltages generates a specific tension field. When that tension is not resolved in one generation, it is transmitted to the next as a conflict instruction. Below all active tensions between {name} and the loaded lineage are mapped, identifying the type of pressure each pair generates in the family field and its impact on the consultant\'s field.',
    espejoIdent:'IDENTICAL MIRROR', parTesla:'TESLA PAIR (sum=9)', complementoFunc:'FUNCTIONAL COMPLEMENT',
    impactoLabel:'IMPACT: ',
    nodoMaestroLabel:'MASTER NODE OF THE CONSULTANT',
    nodoMaestroBody:'Node {nodo} is the point of maximum pressure in {name}\'s fractal ladder. In this year, the {grupo} field of Voltage {voltajeA} reaches its resonance peak with the transgenerational frequency of the lineage. It is not a lucky or unlucky year — it is a year of maximum data density: the system tries to process the largest volume of ancestral information in the shortest time possible. If {name} has no active protocol, this year generates crisis. If an active protocol is in place, it generates the most significant quantum leap of their life.',
    nodoMaestroBodyConEspejos:' In this same node coincide: {espejos} — multiple channel pressure activated.',
    presionCanalMultiple:'MULTIPLE CHANNEL PRESSURE AT THIS NODE',
    ventanaFractal:'FRACTAL WINDOW OF THE MASTER NODE',
    nodoAnteriorLabel:'PREVIOUS NODE: ', proximoNodoLabel2:'NEXT NODE: ',
    patronRepeticion:'REPETITION PATTERN — THE THREE GREAT CLAN CONFLICTS',
    patronRepeticionBody:'Every lineage operates under three major repetition programmes that are transmitted from generation to generation until a conscious node identifies and interrupts them. These three programmes are the distillation of all unresolved conflicts in {name}\'s tree. They are not character defects — they are survival solutions that the family system installed to protect the clan, which have since expired but continue to run.',
