    mapaRecursos:'RESOURCE MAP — THE HIDDEN GIFT OF THE LINEAGE', mapaRecursosCont:'RESOURCE MAP (CONTINUED)',
    mapaRecursosBody:'Every conflict in the tree has a dark side and a luminous side. The lineage gift is the positive frequency that the same conflict contains when resolved. {name}, your lineage did not only transmit wounds — it also transmitted the most powerful vibrational resources available in your field. Below all the active gifts in {name}\'s tree are mapped: the potential available in the system the moment the resolution of each conflict is activated.',
    donActivo:'ACTIVE GIFT:', misionLinajeLabel:'MISSION IN THE LINEAGE:',
    protocoloAccion:'ACTION PROTOCOL — APPLIED REVERSE ENGINEERING',
    protocoloAccionBody:'{name}, a map without a protocol is a diagnosis without treatment. Below are the technical system intervention steps to turn the data in this report into real transformation. The order matters: the system cannot skip stages. Each step activates the next. The full protocol operates within the temporal framework of the fractal nodes — the goal is to have Step 4 active before the next node {proximoNodo}.',
    paso1Arbol:'IDENTIFY THE ORIGINATING ANCESTOR',
    paso1ArbolDesc:'Locate the first lineage member who lived the root conflict "{conflicto}". It is not necessary to know their full story — it is enough to recognise that this conflict existed before {name}. The identification interrupts the unconscious repetition instruction.',
    paso2Arbol:'HONOUR WITHOUT REPEATING',
    paso2ArbolDesc:'"What you lived was yours, not mine. I honour your story without continuing it." This phrase is not a ritual — it is a reprogramming instruction for the emotional field. The family system interprets the honouring as resolution of the pending conflict.',
    paso3Arbol:'ACTIVATE THE OPPOSITE GIFT',
    paso3ArbolDesc:'The distortion is deactivated by activating the gift in real action: "{don}". Recognising it is not enough — it must be expressed in concrete actions. Each time {name} exercises their genuine gift, the system registers an update and reduces the pressure of the inherited conflict.',
    paso4Arbol:'CALIBRATE THE BIOLOGICAL TERMINAL',
    paso4ArbolDesc:'The body is the last storage level of the conflict. When steps 1–3 are activated, the {terminal} terminal begins to release the accumulated charge. It is normal to experience emotional detox symptoms during this process. These are not signs of worsening — they are signs of release.',
    paso5Arbol:'INSTALL THE NEW PROGRAMME',
    paso5ArbolDesc:'The new lineage programme for {name} is summarised as: "{mision}". This is the instruction that replaces the original conflict in the family field. When {name} lives it consciously, they become the first node in the tree to transmit this frequency to future generations.',
    calendarioIntervencion:'INTERVENTION CALENDAR — PRIORITY ACTION WINDOWS',
    calendarioBody:'MECF does not work in linear time — it works in fractal time. The most effective intervention windows are the 6 months before and after each node of {name}. Outside those windows, the system field offers natural resistance. During those windows, the same action has multiplied potency due to the field resonance. Below are the intervention windows calculated for {name}\'s current cycle, with the specific task for each window based on the {archNom} archetype.',
